---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { withLocalePath } from '../../i18n/locale';

const homeHref = withLocalePath('/', 'ru');
const privacyHref = withLocalePath('/datenschutz', 'en');
---

<BaseLayout
	locale="ru"
	title="General terms (brokerage)"
	description="General terms for brokerage and advisory services Prime Realty — courtesy English overview; German originals govern where statutory."
>
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 md:py-16">
		<article class="glass-panel px-8 py-10 md:px-10 md:py-14">
			<h1 class="font-heading-display text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 md:text-4xl">
				General terms (brokerage)
			</h1>
			<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600">Version: December 2025</p>
			<p class="mt-6 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
				These terms govern brokerage and advisory relationships between Prime Realty and its clients concerning real
				property. Mandatory consumer laws in Germany remain unaffected.
			</p>

			<div class="mt-14 space-y-12 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
				<section>
					<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">§ 1 Scope</h2>
					<p class="mt-4">
						<strong class="text-gray-900">(1)</strong> These terms apply to contracts on brokerage/advisory relating to
						property between Prime Realty (“broker”) and the client.
					</p>
					<p class="mt-4">
						<strong class="text-gray-900">(2)</strong> Diverging general terms of the client apply only if expressly
						accepted in writing.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">§ 2 Scope of performance</h2>
					<p class="mt-4">
						<strong class="text-gray-900">(1)</strong> We identify suitable properties / transactions and advise as agreed.
					</p>
					<p class="mt-4">
						<strong class="text-gray-900">(2)</strong> We may, but must not where not agreed, provide comprehensive
						due‑diligence beyond contractually stipulated scope.
					</p>
					<p class="mt-4">
						<strong class="text-gray-900">(3)</strong> No guarantee that a transaction will conclude successfully.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">§ 3 Commission</h2>
					<p class="mt-4">
						<strong class="text-gray-900">(1)</strong> A commission entitlement arises when a purchase/reservation agreement
						mediated through us legally takes effect—subject to the individual engagement clause.
					</p>
					<p class="mt-4">
						<strong class="text-gray-900">(2)</strong> Rates are agreed individually and memorialised.
					</p>
					<p class="mt-4">
						<strong class="text-gray-900">(3)</strong> Fees are payable as agreed upon contract maturity, generally on
						purchase-price basis unless otherwise fixed.
					</p>
					<p class="mt-4">
						<strong class="text-gray-900">(4)</strong> Statutory VAT applies additionally where applicable.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">§ 4 Client duties</h2>
					<p class="mt-4">
						<strong class="text-gray-900">(1)</strong> Inform us promptly of facts material to brokerage.
					</p>
					<p class="mt-4">
						<strong class="text-gray-900">(2)</strong> Treat information disclosed by us confidentially unless lawfully
						shareable with counter-parties/advisers involved in intended transaction.
					</p>
					<p class="mt-4">
						<strong class="text-gray-900">(3)</strong> Notify us immediately of contract negotiations/signing arising
						from our introductions.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">§ 5 Liability</h2>
					<p class="mt-4">
						<strong class="text-gray-900">(1)</strong> Unlimited liability per mandatory law including intent/gross negligence and injury.
					</p>
					<p class="mt-4">
						<strong class="text-gray-900">(2)</strong> For slight negligence we are liable only for breach of cardinal
						obligations (loss typical and foreseeable unless otherwise mandatory).
					</p>
					<p class="mt-4">
						<strong class="text-gray-900">(3)</strong> Further liability excluded per applicable German standards.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">§ 6 Duration and termination</h2>
					<p class="mt-4">
						<strong class="text-gray-900">(1)</strong> Engagements typically run indefinitely unless expressly fixed duration.
					</p>
					<p class="mt-4">
						<strong class="text-gray-900">(2)</strong> Ordinary termination observing 14‑day notice unless contract provides otherwise.
					</p>
					<p class="mt-4">
						<strong class="text-gray-900">(3)</strong> Termination for good cause remains unaffected.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">§ 7 Data protection</h2>
					<p class="mt-4">
						Data processing complies with GDPR; details in our{' '}
						<a href={privacyHref} class="text-accent hover:text-accent-muted">privacy policy</a>.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">§ 8 Final provisions</h2>
					<p class="mt-4">
						<strong class="text-gray-900">(1)</strong> German law excluding UN CISG sales convention.
					</p>
					<p class="mt-4">
						<strong class="text-gray-900">(2)</strong> Place of performance/jurisdiction pursuant to statute and permissible agreement.
					</p>
					<p class="mt-4">
						<strong class="text-gray-900">(3)</strong> Severability clause.
					</p>
				</section>
			</div>

			<p class="mt-14">
				<a href={homeHref} class="text-sm font-semibold text-amber-900 hover:text-amber-950">← Back to home</a>
			</p>
		</article>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>
